            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tecuanimeh tlen mochiuhqueh tlapiyalmeh tlen Canis, achtohui huallayayah ipan lupus Canis; zanpampa tlatehtemoliztli yancuic quihtoa huallohuih tlen lobos tenextiqueh huan chichimeh tlapiyalmeh tlen quence cehca eliyayah ica tlen huahcauhquiya, naman ayoconcah. Chichimeh quipiyah ehelihuiz inintlachiyaliz huan ininhuexca, huan oncah quence 400 tlamantli chichimeh (razas). Nochi chichimeh tlen elqueh tlapiyalmeh huallohuih pan cencah tlamantli tecuani tlen huahcapatl. Quipiya 12,000 xihuitl, nentoc huanya macehualmeh quence tlapeuhquetl, tlamocuitlahuihquetl huan quence tlapalehuihquehtl ica ichcameh huan torohmeh. Naman, chichimeh quimanextiah ce tlamantli tlahuel cualli quence tlatlepanittah huan teicneliah, zanpampa, ipan cequi canahya moixnextiah quence axcencah icamac huan quen monemiltia.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Eastern Huasteca Nahuatl</Note_Language>
